      <h1 class="title is-2">Creating a mailbox</h1>

      This should be pretty straighforward.
      <ul>
        <li>Hit the the plus button on the left</li>
        <li>Add a list of fields that you would like to accept in your form</li>
        <li>Set redirect url</li>
        <li>Optionally set a reply message which will be send to the user who submitted your form</li>
      </ul>

