      <h1 class="title is-2">Form code</h1>

        After specifying the allowed fields of your form and saving you should get a form code.<br/>
        Here's an example of how it might look like if you specified <code>email, subject, body</code>.<br/><br/>

        You can update it and add some styles but <strong>keep the parts surrounded with a red rectangular</strong>.<br/>
        Also keep the name properties of the inputs. <code>name="email"</code>, <code>name="subject"</code>, <code>name="body"</code> etc.<br/>
        But feel free to change other attributes like <code>type</code>

